🚨 @supercrossfutures , an AMA National Championship will resume in 2022 with the sole focus on the 250SX Futures Class. Athletes can begin to qualify starting in October at select primary events spread across the country. Eligible athletes will then advance to a second round of qualifying set to take place at an upcoming Monster Energy AMA Supercross event during the 2022 season to compete then for the Championship at @riceecclesstadium on May 7, 2022.
